name: Zillow Rent Index (Cities): Rentals ZRI Per Sq. Ft. (All Homes) - Raymondville, TX
description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of rentals zri per sq. ft. (all homes) within the city of Raymondville, TX. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
